<HEADLINE> More Obstacles in Bankruptcy Bill </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
	WASHINGTON (AP) -- As some Democrats denounce a Senate bankruptcy  
bill, saying it favors credit card companies at the expense of 
families, a dispute over abortion could imperil the legislation. 
